    "detail": "The room was very tidy and clean. Lockers were provided inside the room. Room key supposed to slot near the lamp to have electricity for each bed allocated. Felt that's not user friendly as one cannot charge their portables and equipment if they were to go to the toilet as the room key is needed to go into the room. Overall is okay. It doesn't provide breakfast but small snacks in the morning with drinks at the roof top. There's laundry room if one needs to do laundry. Hotel is accessible from Taichung Station, about 5-10minutes walk. Shared toilets were clean. Toiletries such as Shampoo & Bathing Gel were available in the toilets as well as hair dryers. Will consider to book this place again! Good for solo travellers and group travellers.",
